WE PUT EVERYTHING
BUSINESS TRAVELERS
WANT IN JUST
ONE LETTER.
INTRODUCING TWQ BUSINESS SERVICE.
At TWA, we know what business travelers want from an airline. And
we've put it all in our TWQ
* Business Service, currently available
from St. Louis to/from Chicago-O'Hare, New York-La Guardia and
Washington National with more markets to come. The "Q" is what
makes it different, with advantages like:
uick service, with close-in permanent gates and Trans World®
Electronic Ticketing at the gate.
Quality treatment, including preferred coach seating to assure
that the first several rows of coach are reserved for Platinum
and Red cardholders. Plus dedicated representatives assigned
to TWQ gates specifically to assist business travelers.
Quantity of conveniences, like first-flight-out/last-flight-in
schedules from Chicago, New York and Washington, D.C. to
St. Louis, and more daily service than any other airline. We'll
even provide complimentary Wall Street Journals on morning
TWQ flights.
One letter, with so many benefits. And look for more TWQ services
to come. Because as long as you're traveling on business, we'll make it
our business to earn yours.
TWQ
BUSINESS SERVICE
WE WANT TO BE YOUR AIRLINE.
TWA
6.413.225
